<%- include("partials/header") -%>

<section class="page-content">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <h1 class="main-h1">Denver Air Quality Monitor</h1>
    <h2 class="main-h2">This site uses data from Open Weather and IQAir to monitor air quality in Denver, Colorado.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="description">
    <p> When this website is opened it automatically checks the current AQI for Denver, CO.
      If the AQI exceeds a score of 100, an email is sent to the governor's office.
      This emails functions as an alert to show that Colorado residents are currently breathing air that is considered harmful to all ages,
      and provides resources and steps by which elected officials can help.
      This site will also serve as a hub for resources related to air quality standards within Colorado and the USA.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container iqAir">
    <h2>Current Conditions</h2>
    <div class="iqAir-widget" name="airvisual_widget" key="<%= iqAirWidgetKey %>"></div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://widget.iqair.com/script/widget_v3.0.js"></script>
    <div class="openWeather table-responsive">
      <table class="pollutant-table table table-bordered">
        <caption>Atmospheric pollution levels </caption>
        <thead>
          <th scope="col"></th>
          <th scope="col">Carbon Monoxide <br> CO </th>
          <th scope="col">Nitrogen Monoxide<br> NO </th>
          <th scope="col">Nitrogen Dioxide<br>NO<sub>2</sub></th>
          <th scope="col">Ozone <br> O <sub>3</sub></th>
          <th scope="col">Sulphur Dioxide<br>SO<sub>2</sub></th>
          <th scope="col">Ammonia<br>NH<sub>3</sub></th>
          <th scope="col">Particulates<br>PM<sub>2.5</sub></th>
          <th scope="col">Particulates<br>PM<sub>10</sub></th>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">Î¼g/m<sup>3</sup>:</th>
            <td><%= co %></td>
            <td><%= no %></td>
            <td><%= no2 %></td>
            <td><%= o3 %></td>
            <td><%= so2 %></td>
            <td><%= nh3 %></td>
            <td><%= pm25 %></td>
            <td><%= pm10 %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="open-weather-credit">Levels provided by <a href="https://openweathermap.org/">OpenWeather</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</body>

</html>

<%- include("partials/footer") -%>
